Happy 4th everybody !!!!  I decided to do yard work and build another  box. 
 This one is changed some stuff on the board.  I changed to a  100k pot, so 
i swapped out the 47uf caps with 100uf and changed the 560R to a  10k 
resistor.

It works fantastic on AM, but FM needs some work.  Not sure what to do  
now.....run 2 separate boards?  Maybe one on sine wave and one on  
triangle.....that&#39;s an idea !!!

At 21 seconds on AM &quot;Princess-----Help-----Earth&quot;

S-H



